Happy Hour: The South River Road Sessions is an EP by Uncle Kracker. It was released on June 22, 2010 under Atlantic Records. The EP features country versions of select tracks from Kracker's Happy Hour album, and Letter To My Daughters from his second album No Stranger to Shame.[1] South River Road is an actual road in Harrison Twp. MI where he grew up and attended high school.
